1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:09,000
Taking walks and playing games when there's sunny weather

2
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:15,000
If there's rain, they're singing songs or reading books together

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:21,000
Every day just has a way of feeling extra lucky

4
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,000
When you spend it with a friend, just like Bjorn and Bucky

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,000
Just like Bjorn and Bucky!

6
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:35,000
Just the right size!

7
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,000
Nice try! Almost!

8
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:44,000
I'm telling you, the trolls are a trillion percent real

9
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:46,000
Sure they are!

10
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:49,000
They're as big as mountains

11
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:52,000
And terribly mean and ugly

12
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Hey Franny, why aren't you eating cherries? Don't you like them?

13
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:58,000
I love them, but I can't reach them

14
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:03,000
Alrighty then! You know, this tree would barely come up to a troll's knees

15
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:07,000
You guys never change! You care more about trolls or whatever than me!

16
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:10,000
Don't be silly! We care about you, Franny!

17
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:14,000
Hey, trolls don't even exist! But you're completely real!

18
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:19,000
Oh, Franny! I think I know what can be done to help you!

19
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:25,000
Hey, we're gonna build Franny something! A fancy ladder just for her so she can reach the cherries!

20
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,000
Awesome plan!

21
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:35,000
My workshop is out of bounds for little kids!

22
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:38,000
Hey, why don't you go swing or something? We'll be right back!

23
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:42,000
Bjorn, close the curtains! This is gonna be awesome!

24
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:47,000
No little kids! That's all I ever hear!

25
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:52,000
I'm sick of being little!

26
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:00,000
Flying through the sky

27
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:02,000
Like a furry butterfly

28
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:05,000
She's so cool, I'll tell you why

29
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:08,000
She's Franny the Cool Big Fox!

30
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,000
I am!

31
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:22,000
Ladders are okay! But this'll be way cool!

32
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,000
Phew!

33
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:35,000
Well, it's done! The larger charger!

34
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,000
Hey!

35
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,000
Where's Fran?

36
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,000
The trolls ate her!

37
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,000
Uh, she's probably picking flowers somewhere!

38
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:43,000
Or trying to pick cherries! Let's go find her!

39
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,000
New invention?

40
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:46,000
Larger charger, huh?

41
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:48,000
I wonder if it'll make me bigger!

42
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,000
Hey! What happened to me?

43
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:56,000
Where could Franny have possibly gone?

44
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:58,000
That girl's always so much trouble!

45
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,000
It's a...

46
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,000
Troll!

47
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,000
Not a troll!

48
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,000
It's Franny, guys!

49
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,000
Franny, guys!

50
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,000
Franny, guys!

51
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,000
Troll!

52
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,000
Troll!

53
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,000
Guys!

54
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,000
Up here!

55
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:20,000
I know you're in there somewhere!

56
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:30,000
Eeny, meeny, miny, miny, yo!

57
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,000
This is getting silly!

58
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,000
Come here!

59
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,000
Look, it's...

60
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,000
Franny!

61
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,000
Franny!

62
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,000
Franny!

63
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,000
There!

64
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:45,000
So you used the larger charger without even asking first!

65
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:49,000
I just wanted to be big enough so you guys would have to notice me!

66
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:52,000
Well, you're certainly hard to miss like this!

67
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,000
Don't be upset,

68
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,000
Don't be upset, Franny!

69
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:57,000
We'll think of a way to help!

70
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,000
I don't wanna be a troll!

71
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,000
Whoa!

72
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,000
Just stop crying!

73
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:05,000
You're acting like a big baby!

74
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:08,000
I can't help it!

75
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:13,000
I wanna be little, like I was before!

76
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:15,000
I don't wanna be big!

77
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:20,000
I don't wanna be a whale pox!

78
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,000
Franny!

79
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,000
Franny!

80
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,000
Huh?

81
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:28,000
We made something so you won't be too small anymore!

82
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,000
Bucky, it's time!

83
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:31,000
Get Franny's big surprise, please!

84
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,000
Oh, please!

85
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,000
Just not the larger charger!

86
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,000
I've never heard of that!

87
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,000
But this is yours!

88
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:38,000
To get at High Branches, the Super Climatron!

89
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:41,000
You made me a ladder of my very own?

90
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,000
A ladder?

91
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,000
This is no ordinary ladder!

92
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:47,000
It's a Super Climatron with an advanced platform system

93
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:50,000
and dual bear transport action!

94
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:55,000
So, Franny, you can pick all the yummy cherries that you'd like now!

95
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,000
Come try it out!

96
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:07,000
Yeah! Climatronic, baby!

97
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:10,000
Oh, I'm telling you!

98
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,000
The trolls are absolutely for real!

99
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,000
Uh-huh!

100
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:15,000
Yeah, sure they are!

101
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:20,000
I suppose that trolls can just rip trees right from the ground, too!

102
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,000
Yeah, of course!

103
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,000
Silly bears!

104
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:25,000
I just adore you!

